OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FRather cloudy with a few
OL,6,Fspots of light rain, but some drier,
OL,7,Fbrighter spells developing in the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Outbreaks of rain will then
OL,9,Fspread northeast during the evening
OL,10,Fand overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,13,Ffairly unsettled and changeable few
OL,14,Fdays with a series of showery or
OL,15,Foccasionally more persistent bands of
OL,16,Frain spreading up from the southwest
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
